name: Sunny Beach Girls
description:
Sunny Beach Girls is a simple classic 2048 game with cute girls on the beach! Try to relax and win this puzzle game.

Instructions:

Sunny Beach Girls is a classic puzzle game. You should move slides with arrows to reach 2048.


Key Features:

All girls in the game are over 18 years old.
Different styles of girls
Full nudity
Puzzles
Nice relaxing music
